## 5. Flask bridge (mw-backend)

File: `mw-backend/orschell_ecommerce_blueprint.py`

Copy `bridge_blueprint_template.py`, set:
```python
PREFIX   = "demos/orschell-excavating-e-commerce-full/api"
UPSTREAM = "http://127.0.0.1:3742"
```

Register in `server.py` after the last blueprint:
```python
# Orschell E-Commerce demo bridge
from orschell_ecommerce_blueprint import bridge_bp as orschell_bp
app.register_blueprint(orschell_bp)
```

Public API base URL: `https://api.michaelwegter.com/demos/orschell-excavating-e-commerce-full/api`

Frontend `src/api/client.ts` base URL:
```typescript
const BASE = 'https://api.michaelwegter.com/demos/orschell-excavating-e-commerce-full/api';
```

