## 8. Design tokens (exact CSS custom properties)

```css
:root {
  /* Backgrounds */
  --bg-base:    #1C1F24;
  --bg-surface: #2B2E35;
  --bg-card:    #33373F;
  --bg-input:   #22262D;

  /* Brand */
  --accent-orange: #F76B10;
  --accent-orange-hover: #D95E0D;
  --accent-yellow: #FFD600;

  /* Text */
  --text-primary: #EAEAEA;
  --text-muted:   #9AA0AB;
  --text-inverse: #0D0F12;

  /* Status */
  --color-danger:  #E84040;
  --color-success: #27AE60;
  --color-warning: #F5A623;

  /* Borders */
  --border-default: 1px solid #3E434D;
  --border-accent:  2px solid #F76B10;
  --radius: 3px;

  /* Motifs */
  --hazard-stripe: repeating-linear-gradient(
    -45deg,
    #F76B10,
    #F76B10 10px,
    #1C1F24 10px,
    #1C1F24 20px
  );
}
```

Google Fonts import (in `index.html` `<head>`):
```html
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@600;700;900&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
```

```css
font-family headings: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;  /* bold, uppercase, letter-spacing: 0.04em */
font-family body:     'Inter', sans-serif;
```

Motif usage patterns:
- **Hazard dividers**: `<div style="background: var(--hazard-stripe); height: 4px">` between hero + content sections
- **Category badge pills**: `border: 1px solid var(--accent-orange); border-radius: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 11px; font-family: Barlow Condensed; letter-spacing: 0.08em; padding: 2px 8px; color: var(--accent-orange)`
- **Price tag**: `color: var(--accent-orange); font: 700 22px 'Barlow Condensed'`
- **CTA button**: `background: var(--accent-orange); color: #fff; border: none; font: 700 14px 'Barlow Condensed'; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: var(--radius)`
- **Low-stock badge**: `background: var(--color-danger); color: #fff; font-size: 11px; padding: 2px 6px`
- **Stock-OK badge**: `background: var(--color-success); color: #fff`
- **2px card borders**: `border: 2px solid #3E434D` with `:hover` -> `border-color: var(--accent-orange)`
- **Admin sidebar**: dark `#1C1F24` with `border-right: 2px solid var(--accent-orange)` active state

