## 12. SQLite-to-Postgres delta (for deck slide)

The demo schema is already Postgres-compatible. Driver swap for production:
- Remove `node:sqlite` import
- `npm install pg @types/pg`
- Replace `DatabaseSync` with `new Pool({ connectionString: process.env.DATABASE_URL })`
- `.all()` -> `(await pool.query(sql, params)).rows`
- `.get()` -> `(await pool.query(sql, params)).rows[0]`
- `.run()` -> `await pool.query(sql, params)` (uses `result.rowCount` for changes)
- `db.exec()` -> `await pool.query(ddl)`

