- decisions: port 3742 (adverteyes = 3741, no conflict); bridge prefix = `demos/orschell-excavating-e-commerce-full/api`; tsconfig target ES2022 for node:sqlite; picsum.photos seed by SKU for images
- next needs: demo-builder reads this file + planner.out for schema/endpoints/seed data; builds Surface backend first (npm install, tsc, register service), then Vite frontend, then bridge blueprint
